This is what you have to do when saving the video:
ani_.save(&lsquo;output.avi&rsquo;, fps=args_[&lsquo;fps&rsquo;], savefig_kwargs = { &lsquo;transparent&rsquo; : True , &lsquo;facecolor&rsquo; : &lsquo;black&rsquo;Â }
Argument savefig_kwargs is the key parameter. It is applied to savefig which is called every time a frame is saved into video file. Ref: http://matplotlib.org/api/animation_api.html
